{"word":"αἰψηρός","slug":"αἰψηρός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n2811\" key=\"ai)yhro/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">αἰψηρός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ά</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">αἶψα</etym>) <sense id=\"n2811.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">quick, speedy, sudden</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἰψηρὸς δὲ κόρος κρυεροῖο γόοιο</foreign> satiety in grief <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">comes soon</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:103\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.103</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λῦσεν δ᾽ ἀγορὴν αἰψηρήν</foreign> he dismissed the assembly <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in haste</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:276\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.276</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:257\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.257</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Ζεφύρου αἰ. πνοαί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg005:2:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Parth.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.17</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quot